{"tid":1658545,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[不分和勇]我諗大家好似唔記得左一啲野[/齊上齊落]","createTime":"2019-10-16T13:51:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T16:28:32.000Z","uid":313764,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"55505adf7b014e501ed78035845a6f0f98d30ffd","tid":1658545,"uid":313764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T13:51:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BK9K8td.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBK9K8td.png&h=2c93cdf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/抗爭理論-運動正值抗爭週期關鍵時刻-勇武及和理非切勿分化/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E7%90%86%E8%AB%96-%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95%E6%AD%A3%E5%80%BC%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E9%80%B1%E6%9C%9F%E9%97%9C%E9%8D%B5%E6%99%82%E5%88%BB-%E5%8B%87%E6%AD%A6%E5%8F%8A%E5%92%8C%E7%90%86%E9%9D%9E%E5%88%87%E5%8B%BF%E5%88%86%E5%8C%96%2F&d=Wg3pkMW64ksxbb%2FAt9Sry77zmW0KSjJ%2FkJHMgTQKA%2BU%3D&h=3a570c3f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E7%90%86%E8%AB%96-%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95%E6%AD%A3%E5%80%BC%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E9%80%B1%E6%9C%9F%E9%97%9C%E9%8D%B5%E6%99%82%E5%88%BB-%E5%8B%87%E6%AD%A6%E5%8F%8A%E5%92%8C%E7%90%86%E9%9D%9E%E5%88%87%E5%8B%BF%E5%88%86%E5%8C%96%2F&h=b4e25cde\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/抗爭理論-運動正值抗爭週期關鍵時刻-勇武及和理非切勿分化/</a><br />\n<br />\n我引用文中幾句說話<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>〝 但是我們不要讓<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「思考」</strong></span>變成<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「爭辯」</strong></span>，繼而變成<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「分裂」</strong></span>〞</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>若然政府不願意妥協，便會選擇<br />\n<br />\n(1). 拉攏<br />\n<br />\n(2). 鎮壓<br />\n<br />\n(3). 分化的措施。<br />\n<br />\n**********************************************<br />\n<br />\n(1) 使部分溫和派放棄運動走入體制進行改革<br />\n<br />\n(2) 使抗爭者精疲力竭<br />\n<br />\n(3)使抗爭者出現分化和矛盾。抗爭者的疲憊感和挫敗也會促成內部分歧，包括戰略、抗爭手段和價值觀（意識形態）的爭議。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>事實上，書生認為雨傘運動的失敗原因之一，就是中後期當政府使用<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「拖字訣」</strong></span>時，反對陣營出現「左／右」的巨大紛爭和競爭，促成運動後期的迅速消散。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一開始明明講好左和勇不分，勇武前線抗爭,召喚神獸,裝修...etc ; 和理非後邊幫手文宣，幫手解釋點解勇武要咁做，爭取「靚畫面」為國際線宣傳( eg : 200萬人大遊行, 修頓球場燒jersey)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但點解去到今日係出邊d post 仲係有人話20號應該和理非定勇武抗爭?</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">**********</span><br />\n「兄弟爬山，各自努力」正正代表住大家有共識，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>就算成個運動出現你唔認同既事，但只要大家目標都係為左「攻頂」既話就點都要支持，互相配合。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n記住，槍口要瞄準政權同警隊而唔係自己人<br />\n<br />\n最後提一提大家20號用自己方法出黎抗爭，爭取自己想要既野。<br />\n<br />\n最後最後，如果你係四個月黎都未做過d 咩，但又心大心細想為香港/自己將來做d 野既話，請你立即用自己最容易做到既方法行動，在為時已晚之前。"},{"pid":"2350c8c751310e7fbbf52e52f4e89ff34ff28648","tid":1658545,"uid":209543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T13:52:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1397a760d6867e5082ea628ee5c467ad01b202ed","tid":1658545,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T13:53:03.000Z","msg":"屌你老母岑子杰單野我要響國際新聞見到！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1658212\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1658212</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n全世界同我落<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#PrayForJimmy</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記得寫係ProBeijing Red Thugs 做！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class